## 📌 3. 기술 스택 상세

### Front-End (frontend/)
| 항목 | 기술 |
|------|------|
| Framework | React Native + Expo (SDK 54) |
| State | Zustand |
| Navigation | React Navigation (Bottom Tabs) |
| Camera | expo-camera, expo-image-picker |
| Styling | StyleSheet (타임라인은 CSS 트리구조) |
| Network | Axios |

### Back-End (backend/)
| 항목 | 기술 |
|------|------|
| Framework | Node.js + Express.js |
| File Upload | Multer |
| Database | MongoDB + Mongoose |
| AI/Vision | Google Cloud Vision API (예정) |
| LLM | OpenAI API (예정) |

